setDetails.setDescription: The Supercash Active Fund (SCASH) is a medium-term focused DeFi fund that exposes investors to the market on uptrends and protects on downtrends. It uses a trading/signaling strategy to buy or sell assets account to an optimized trend following algorithmm, which tries to keep the fund allocated on a set of cryptoassets (e.g. ETH, BNB, BTC, ...) during all the uptrend, as well as realocating the fund to dollar (e.g USDC) to protect the fund during downtrends.
